01:33.106 --> 01:35.350
graduating class of 92. So our department will not 
only have the management problems we presently

01:37.032 --> 01:49.789
face, but we are going to be serving two programs at 
one time for the next three years. And this will be

01:52.301 --> 01:54.744
just your department, pretty much, won't it? I 
mean, it'll affect this one the majority. It'll

01:56.667 --> 02:03.657
affect, for example, educational psychology 
would be affected by those service courses that

01:56.667 --> 02:03.657
