Dean came here in 1980, I came here in 1981. I knew 
something about Texas and I knew something about

05:10.675 --> 05:14.138
the makeup of Texas. And so I was quite surprised, 
I'd say relatively surprised, that when I came

05:14.779 --> 05:30.295
here we did not have any program in the department 
that addressed the needs of the minorities in the

05:14.779 --> 05:30.295
state of Texas.

